msgid ""
"A new modular Python API is made available, public and documented. This is a "
"real API, with building blocks that are already used to build the Conan "
"built-in commands, but that will allow further extensions. There are sub-"
"APIs for different functional groups, like ``api.list``, ``api.search``, "
"``api.remove``, ``api.profile``, ``api.graph``, ``api.upload``, ``api."
"remotes``, etc. that will allow to implement advanced user flows, "
"functionality and automation."
